dml.team5.antlr

Class PLSQLBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • dml.team5.antlr.PLSQLBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PLSQLListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SelectedElementListener, TableListener

    public class PLSQLBaseListener
extends Object
implements PLSQLListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of PLSQLListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
